-The device has the \f(CW\*(C`ELPM R\f(CIn\f(CW,Z\*(C'\fR and \f(CW\*(C`ELPM
-R\f(CIn\f(CW,Z+\*(C'\fR instructions.
-.ie n .IP """_\|_AVR_HAVE_LPMX_\|_""" 4
