-.el .IP "\f(CW_\|_AVR_HAVE_16BIT_SP_\|_\fR" 4
-.IX Item "__AVR_HAVE_16BIT_SP__"
-.PD
-The stack pointer (\s-1SP\s0) register is treated as 8\-bit respectively
