-.PD 0
-.IP "\fBgnu++2a\fR" 4
-.IX Item "gnu++2a"
-.PD
-\&\s-1GNU\s0 dialect of \fB\-std=c++20\fR.
-Support is experimental, and could change in incompatible ways in
