-The name \fBgnu++2a\fR is deprecated.
-.IP "\fBc++2b\fR" 4
-.IX Item "c++2b"
-.PD 0
-.IP "\fBc++23\fR" 4
-.IX Item "c++23"
-.PD
-The next revision of the \s-1ISO \*(C+\s0 standard, planned for
-2023.  Support is highly experimental, and will almost certainly
