-.IP "za64rs" 4
-.IX Item "za64rs"
-\&\f(CW@tab\fR 1.0
-\&\f(CW@tab\fR Reservation set size of 64 bytes.
-.IP "za128rs" 4
-.IX Item "za128rs"
-\&\f(CW@tab\fR 1.0
-\&\f(CW@tab\fR Reservation set size of 128 bytes.
-.IP "zawrs" 4
-.IX Item "zawrs"
-\&\f(CW@tab\fR 1.0
-\&\f(CW@tab\fR Wait-on-reservation-set extension.
-.IP "zba" 4
-.IX Item "zba"
-\&\f(CW@tab\fR 1.0
-\&\f(CW@tab\fR Address calculation extension.
