-notebooks.
-.IP "\fBpentium4\fR" 4
-.IX Item "pentium4"
-.PD 0
-.IP "\fBpentium4m\fR" 4
-.IX Item "pentium4m"
-.PD
-Intel Pentium 4 \s-1CPU\s0 with \s-1MMX, SSE, SSE2\s0 and \s-1FXSR\s0 instruction set support.
